To test server and client' s work, run first ServerMainRecover, then ClientMain1
To test server and client's work with Recover messages feature, run ServerMainRecover,
 then ClientMain1 and ClientMain2

To test the division by team, run first ServerMainRecoverTeam, then ClientMain1 
and ClientMain2(they are in the same team);

If you want test two clients in different teams(That don't communicate between themselves, run first ServerMainRecoverTeam,
 then ClientMain1 and ClientMain2DifferentTeam
 
 
